"```sql\nSELECT d.forename, d.surname, lt.time\nFROM drivers d\nJOIN lapTimes lt ON d.driverId = lt.driverId\nWHERE d.nationality = 'Spanish' AND YEAR(d.dob) < 1982\nORDER BY lt.time DESC\nLIMIT 10;\n```\n\nThis SQL query selects the forename, surname, and lap time of Spanish drivers who were born before 1982. It orders the results by the lap time in descending order to get the latest lap times and limits the output to the top 10 results."